source: The modern city of Casablanca was founded by Berber fishermen in the 10th century BCE, and was used by the Phoenicians, Romans, and the Merenids as a strategic port called Anfa.

source: The modern city of Casablanca was founded by Berber fishermen in the 10th century BCE, and was used by the Phoenicians, Romans, and the Merenids as a strategic port called Anfa.

source: The modern city of Casablanca was founded by Berber fishermen in the 10th centuryBCE, and was used by the Phoenicians, Romans, and the Merenids as a strategic port called Anfa.
translation: नवीऩ नकरमाकिय कासापिळाङ्का, पर्पर् मीऩवर्कळाल् 10 आम् नूऱ्ऱाण्टु पिचिइ यिल् निऱुवप्पट्टतु मऱ्ऱुम् पोऩीचियर्कळ्, रोमऩियर्कळ्, मऱ्ऱुम् मेरेऩिट्कळाल् आऩ्ःपा ऎऩ्ऱ मूलोपायत् तुऱैमुकमाक पयऩ्पटुत्तप्पट्टतु.

source: The Three Kingdoms was one of the bloodiest eras in Ancient China’s history thousands of people died fighting to sit in the highest seat in the grand palace at Xi’an.

translation: उलक वॆप्पमयमातलाल् पातिक्कप्पट्ट नाटुकळुक्कु इन्त पातिप्पुकळै चमाळिक्क उतवुम् वकैयिल् ऒरु नितियै मुटिवु चॆय्य इयलुम् ऎऩ U.N. नम्पुकिऱतु.
